---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import BackAndForthSection from '../components/BackAndForthSection.astro';

const title = 'Process | Window Film Philadelphia | Leading Window Film Solutions';
const description = 'Window Film Philadelphia is honored to share our proprietary, time-tested window film process. Schedule your free consultation today!';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} canonical='https://www.windowfilmphiladelphia.net/process/'>
  <section class="page-hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,30,90,0.72), rgba(0,30,90,0.88)), url('/images/2021-10-window-film-process-philadelphia.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Expert Window Film Installation in Philadelphia</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <BackAndForthSection
  heading={'Expert Window Film Installation in Philadelphia'}
  body={'Our team specializes in window film installation in Philadelphia, providing both residential and commercial properties with precise, professional service. Using cutting-edge technology and a time-tested process, we ensure your window film is installed efficiently, with optimal adhesion and performance. Whether you are enhancing privacy, energy efficiency, or security, our installation methods maximize the benefits of your investment while delivering long-lasting results.'}
  imageSrc={'/images/2021-10-window-film-process-philadelphia.jpg'}
  imageAlt={'window-film-process-philadelphia'}
  flip={false}
  altBg={false}
/>

  <BackAndForthSection
  heading={'Step One: Window Film Consultation'}
  body={'We provide either same-day installations or consultations for our clients. During this consultation, our window film contractors will show you all the available options for your property. We’ll discuss your project goals and what investments are best suited for your residential or commercial property. We’re happy to either schedule a future appointment for installation or proceed with a same-day installation based on what’s convenient for you.'}
  imageSrc={'/images/2021-10-window-film-preparation-philadelphia.jpg'}
  imageAlt={'window film preparation philadelphia'}
  flip={true}
  altBg={true}
/>

  <BackAndForthSection
  heading={'Step Two: Window Film Preparation'}
  body={'In order to ensure proper adhesion of your window film, our contractors will prepare your windows by cleaning them. We utilize razor blades and squeegee tools in order to remove any dirt or debris that might be on the interior or exterior of your glass. This helps provide a proper cure and adhesion for your window film.'}
  imageSrc={'/images/2021-10-window-film-installation-philadelphia.jpg'}
  imageAlt={'window film installation philadelphia'}
  flip={false}
  altBg={false}
/>

  <section class="section-pad">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Step Three: Window Film Installation</h2>
    <p>Once your windows and glass doors have been cleaned and prepped, installation takes place. Our contractors custom cut your window film according to each required dimension in order to minimize product waste and create an effective, quick installation. For certain projects, we utilize C-Bond for quicker cure times and optimal adhesion. If you’re interested in utilizing C-Bond for your window film project, please let us know! Once installed, DO NOT CLEAN YOUR WINDOW FILM FOR 30 DAYS. Your window film will need proper time to cure and should be left undisturbed for the full month.</p>
  </div>
</section>

  <section class="section-pad">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Work With Philadelphia’s Trusted Window Film Installation Experts</h2>
    <p>For reliable window film installation in Philadelphia, our team delivers expert solutions tailored to your property. Window Film Philadelphia ensures every installation is precise, professional, and maximizes the performance of your film, whether for energy savings, security, or aesthetic upgrades. Contact us today to schedule your project.</p>
  </div>
</section>

  <section class="cta-strip">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Get Your Free Quote Today</h2>
      <p>Philadelphia&#39;s leading window film contractor. Contact us for a free consultation and estimate.</p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--accent">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
